  "title": "A Council of Moffs and the FLS Question",
  "summary": "In the opulent Moff's Council Chambers atop the Imperial City of Selene, the Jedi Moff Johanna convenes a casual but pointed meeting with fellow Imperium leaders about a slaving and smuggling pipeline running through the Tion Cluster. Drawing on his smuggling past, Axel maps likely hiding spots, while the Falleen Nasiri reveals damning evidence of front companies whose hauls were contracted seventy percent of the time to the shipping giant FLS. Presav Crestian Tarasar, protective of his Caspian citizens and the FLS headquarters in his capital, sharply resists any talk of destroying Caspian-flagged vessels without solid proof, sparring with Nasiri over insinuations of Sarian favoritism. Johanna steers the group toward a measured plan: scouting, surveillance, and a forensic investigation by her slicer and accountant before any action. The meeting ends with Axel volunteering to scout the cluster personally and departing with a parting jab for Crestian and Nasiri to settle their friction.",
